Package etphoneshome.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Collectible
    This class is the parent class of ReesesPieces and PhonePieces.
    Hitbox  
    Level
    Stores all items in a level including, the levelNumber, end coordinate, time-limit, background path, list of obstacles, list of enemies, list of phone pieces, and level image
    Location  
    Obstacle
    This class is used to represent the location for the Obstacle.
    PhonePiece
    this class is for the phone piece collectible needed to win using getters and setters you get and set the width,height, image, location, hitbox and the type of phone piece
    Platform
    This class represents a platform that an Actor can stand on.
    Player
    this class will handle the previous players of the game and the current one for highscore purposes Using getters and setters you can get and set the name and score
    ReesesPieces
    This class is an extension of the Collectible class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PhonePieceType
    Enum storing the constant values for types of phone pieces that can be collected
